mkdir ~/.fonts
cp simsun.ttf ~/.fonts
cd ~/.fonts
mkfontscale
mkfontdir
fc-cache -fv ~/.fonts
fc-list |grep Sim


simsun is bitmap font, and others font like wqy mostly are not
bitmap font, but wqy do have one bitmap font, and it's called
wqy-bitmapfont in archlinux, and xfonts-wqy in debian jessie.
bitmap font display better than other fonts.
